title: Icon Question
body: I did the questions for the summon icon.  I never got my icon and wanted to know what happen???

replies.body: Per the redemption page, it may take some time to roll out the icons.  You should see it unlocked on your account in a few days.  Let me know if you have any questions!
It said after the quiz was done that it could take a few days before the icon will arrive on your account.
